narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Not particularly well taught though definitely not hard as far as languages go at Yale

Fun! The bar is higher than first semester, but still relaxed and fun.NOTE: if for some reason you think you can get away with skipping class all the time, think again. You will get a c or a d without any hesitation. She is cracking down. It is a chill class, and the work is not too bad, so why give up a good grade?
